
##Disable password required linux:
	$ sudo visudo
	Then, search for %admin ALL=(ALL) ALL and replace the line by %admin ALL=(ALL) NOPASSWD: ALL.
	Used shortcut key [CTRL] + [o] and press Enter to save all changes. Next, use shortcut key [CTRL] + [x] to close the file.


##Adding repository(ubuntu):
	$ sudo add-apt-repository "deb [arch=amd64] https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu $(lsb_release -cs) stable"


##CPU avg usage:
	$ sar -u 5

##Privilege permissions with speciofic user and app:
	(here below cloud user 'ubuntu' granted with permissions to docker app)
	$ sudo usermod -a -G docker ubuntu

##Keep spot instacne alive script (if configured threshold of 1 % cpu avg):
	$ while (true); do apt-get update > /dev/null 2>&1;  sleep 3 ; done

##Transfer output to dev null & :
 $ any_command_with_output >>/dev/null 2>&1
 
##Linux web browser:
	$ elinks localhost:80

## Print storage-devices status:
	$ dh -f \ du -f (du printing directory capacity)
## Print Which user am I:
	$ whoami
